                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3z02zv83/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I notice in the Occident that you oppose of the<lb/> course of <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                        ><persName>Eckman</persName></hi> at\n                    <placeName><sic>charleston</sic></placeName> I can assure<lb/> you that you are\n                greatly mistaken if you<lb/> suppose him to be what he pretends to be<lb/> you\n                judged him right when you said you<lb/> liked <sic>consistancy</sic>, he made up his\n                mind to apply<lb/> for the office at <placeName>Charleston</placeName> before he\n                left this city<lb/> it was known for some weeks before he left<lb/> this city that\n                he intended to try &amp; get the office<lb/> he carried letters with him from this\n                city<lb/> which he asked for in order to obtain the<lb/> office at\n                    <placeName>Charleston</placeName>, I tell you Sir if there<lb/> ever was a grand\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">Hypocrite</hi> it is to<lb/> be found in <persName>Julias\n                    Eckman</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yours Respty</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">N Ezekiel</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><sic>Cant</sic> you send the Occident by mail<lb/> as the express bill is too much\n                the postage<lb/> is cheap now &amp; you can direct them<lb/> to the Subscribers or\n                to me as you like</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">N Ezekiel</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3z02zv83/canvas/p2"
                }
